Sentencas: An anode-supported cone-shaped tubular solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) with (Ni0.75Fe0.25-5% MgO)/YSZ anode is prepared and is directly operated on dry and moist CO fuel, respectively.
Titulo: Carbon Monoxide Fueled Cone-Shaped Tubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell with (Ni0.75Fe0.25-5% MgO)/YSZ Anode

Sentencas: At 800 degrees C, the cell exhibits a maximum power density (MPD) of 424 mWcm(-2) for dry CO and 388 mWcm(-2) for moist CO.
Titulo: Carbon Monoxide Fueled Cone-Shaped Tubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell with (Ni0.75Fe0.25-5% MgO)/YSZ Anode

Sentencas: The durability test results show no significant degradation in performance for this kind of cell operated on either dry or moist CO after an operation time of 40 h at a constant current of 83 mA cm(-2) at 800 degrees C, while the cell with Ni/YSZ anode, in comparison, fails rapidly.
Titulo: Carbon Monoxide Fueled Cone-Shaped Tubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell with (Ni0.75Fe0.25-5% MgO)/YSZ Anode
